HEADWORD: Pocketbook
<hw>Pock"et*book`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A small book or
case for carrying papers, money, etc., in the pocket; also, a notebook
for the pocket.</def>⟦br⟧
